my robust mental health.

04:54.127 --> 04:55.863
Mmm, well, I got to go.

04:55.896 --> 04:56.997
I'll, uh, call you later?

04:57.030 --> 04:57.998
Okay.
'Kay.

04:58.031 --> 04:59.833
Mayor Hayes.

05:02.035 --> 05:03.070
Thank you.

05:03.103 --> 05:05.072
She is so cool.

05:05.105 --> 05:07.575
