she accepted, yes.

05:26.494 --> 05:28.462
But she did not forgive me.

05:28.496 --> 05:30.398
Hmm, what do you
say to that?

05:30.431 --> 05:33.501
That you might have
exaggerated your mental health.

05:33.534 --> 05:35.403
Says the woman perched
atop a love triangle.

05:35.436 --> 05:37.971
Hey, I told you,
not anymore.

05:38.005 --> 05:39.373
I made a choice.

05:39.407 --> 05:40.408
I chose me.

05:40.441 --> 05:41.842
Everything is under control.

05:41.875 --> 05:44.712
I can't be a rebound,
so I won't be with George

05:44.745 --> 05:46.447
