05:56.156 --> 05:58.091
Okay.

05:58.125 --> 06:00.994
And meanwhile, you just keep
getting freaky with Wade.

06:01.028 --> 06:01.829
What?

06:01.862 --> 06:03.130
No, I totally stopped
doing that.

06:03.163 --> 06:04.865
Since when?

06:04.898 --> 06:06.434
