06:06.467 --> 06:07.435
Like an hour ago.

06:07.468 --> 06:08.902
See? Under control.

06:11.472 --> 06:12.873
Here you go, everyone.

06:12.906 --> 06:15.175
Oh, elbows
off the table, please.

06:15.208 --> 06:16.610
And, sir, if the sun
gets too bright in here,

06:16.644 --> 06:19.146
feel free to wear
your hat indoors.

06:19.179 --> 06:20.714
If not, let's take it off, okay?

06:20.748 --> 06:23.116
Enjoy.

06:23.150 --> 06:24.985
You gotta fire her.

06:25.018 --> 06:25.986
No, she's...

06:26.019 --> 06:29.423
She's not that bad.

06:29.457 --> 06:30.357
She's the worst waitress
we ever had

06:30.390 --> 06:31.859
and we've never been
known for our service.

06:31.892 --> 06:33.160
I'm bussing all her tables

06:33.193 --> 06:36.129
'cause she refuses
to touch half-chewed food!

06:36.163 --> 06:37.698
See?

06:37.731 --> 06:39.099
Take care of it.

06:39.132 --> 06:40.100
No way.
Not happening.

06:40.133 --> 06:42.169
WALLY:
What, you afraid of her?

06:42.202 --> 06:43.871
Yeah.

06:50.177 --> 06:52.946
Casual day at the law firm?

06:52.980 --> 06:56.750
No, I'm just, uh,
just going fishing.

06:56.784 --> 06:58.051
Good.

06:58.085 --> 06:59.487
I mean, if you like fishing.

06:59.520 --> 07:00.488
And it makes you happy.

07:00.521 --> 07:01.489
Are you happy?

07:01.522 --> 07:02.923
Because I want you to be happy.

07:02.956 --> 07:04.492
And I know I threw
a lot at you last week.

07:04.525 --> 07:05.893
Oh, wait, wait.

07:05.926 --> 07:07.094
You're talking
about when you told me

07:07.127 --> 07:08.095
that you want me
to date other people

07:08.128 --> 07:09.930
instead of you, right?

07:09.963 --> 07:11.064
Yup, that was it then.

07:11.098 --> 07:14.034
Yeah, uh...

07:14.067 --> 07:16.236
That...

07:16.269 --> 07:18.572
