07:18.606 --> 07:22.075
And I'm sorry, you know, it's
that you just got out of a...

07:22.109 --> 07:24.512
15 year relationship,
I know, I was there.

07:28.248 --> 07:32.553
Zoe, I am, uh, not giving
up on the two of us.

07:32.586 --> 07:34.121
See, I'm still hoping that
we'll be together someday,

07:34.154 --> 07:37.257
so I'm just gonna take
this time I got here

07:37.290 --> 07:38.892
and I'm gonna become
the best version of myself

07:38.926 --> 07:43.831
that I possibly can be
because well, you deserve that.

07:43.864 --> 07:46.567
Yes.

07:46.600 --> 07:47.901
So do you.

07:50.771 --> 07:52.005
ZOE:
 I'm bad.

07:52.039 --> 07:54.007
Bad, bad, bad.

07:54.041 --> 07:56.209
You having sex
with Wade isn't bad.

07:56.243 --> 07:57.678
WADE:
Not bad?

07:57.711 --> 07:58.846
I've heard
it's freaking awesome.

07:58.879 --> 08:00.514
Ha, hardly.

08:00.548 --> 08:03.751
And it doesn't even matter
because never again.

08:03.784 --> 08:06.754
Oops, aren't you, uh,

08:06.787 --> 08:09.189
aren't you supposed to say
that after we do it?

08:09.222 --> 08:10.257
ZOE:
No more, Wade.

08:10.290 --> 08:11.692
Lavon, tell him.

08:11.725 --> 08:12.893
Me?

08:12.926 --> 08:14.795
No, no, I-I'm way out of this.

08:14.828 --> 08:15.896
