but I doubt anyone would listen.

08:23.737 --> 08:26.940
This wouldn't, uh, happen to be
about George Tucker, would it?

08:26.974 --> 08:28.041
No.

08:28.075 --> 08:31.912
This is about being the best
version of me I can be.

08:31.945 --> 08:34.214
I told Rose to be
her best self.

08:34.246 --> 08:36.884
George is trying
to be his best self.

08:36.917 --> 08:39.251
