that I don't even like

08:39.285 --> 08:42.690
is hardly me being mine.

08:42.722 --> 08:44.224
Problem is, Doc, you're hooked.

08:44.256 --> 08:45.192
Oh, I am not hooked.

08:45.225 --> 08:47.294
Yeah, you are.

08:47.327 --> 08:49.096
