sex within the next 48 hours.

08:51.231 --> 08:53.200
$50?
Mmm.

08:53.233 --> 08:55.068
Why don't we make it a 100?

08:55.102 --> 08:56.069
Shake on it.

09:00.140 --> 09:01.174
Out!

09:01.208 --> 09:03.110
(Wade laughs)

09:03.143 --> 09:05.846
Two days without you is easy.

09:05.879 --> 09:07.615
I have gone way
longer than that

09:07.648 --> 09:09.016
without sex.

09:09.049 --> 09:10.684
I have gone years.

09:12.886 --> 09:14.287
Yeah.

09:14.321 --> 09:15.856
