of the problem.

09:19.092 --> 09:21.328
(car horn honks)

09:21.361 --> 09:23.664
(seagulls calling)

09:23.697 --> 09:25.265
(birds singing)

09:34.708 --> 09:36.243
JEFFRIES:
Oh, there he is!

09:36.276 --> 09:37.778
There he is now!

09:37.811 --> 09:39.312
Hey, Grandpop, please, okay?

09:39.346 --> 09:41.314
What's going on, y'all?

09:41.348 --> 09:45.218
