10:05.438 --> 10:08.108
Who'll buy my toaster cozies?

10:08.141 --> 10:09.242
No, no, now.

10:09.276 --> 10:10.744
The tourism is just fine, okay?

10:10.778 --> 10:13.246
Just today, a-a women's
pro-beach volleyball team

10:13.280 --> 10:15.115
