through your fingers

10:18.285 --> 10:19.286
like an Auburn running back!

10:19.319 --> 10:21.021
I have been silent long enough!

10:21.054 --> 10:23.657
Grandpa, when have you ever
been silent for five minutes?

10:23.691 --> 10:24.892
No, there is an
election coming up,

10:24.925 --> 10:27.060
and I intend to run
against Mayor Hayes,

10:27.094 --> 10:28.862
and I intend to win!

10:28.896 --> 10:30.731
Okay, Grandpa.
Hmm.

10:30.764 --> 10:31.832
Let's go get some breakfast,
okay?

10:31.865 --> 10:33.166
Let's get you
something to eat.

10:33.200 --> 10:35.102
