might have any advice

12:08.061 --> 12:11.098
I can give to Wally
on how to fire her?

12:11.131 --> 12:12.399
Yeah.

12:12.432 --> 12:14.367
Yeah, I do.

12:14.401 --> 12:15.368
Don't.

12:15.402 --> 12:17.805
I thought so.

12:17.838 --> 12:19.139
All right.

12:22.242 --> 12:25.445
Ruby didn't have to blindside me
with that Southern Living news.

12:25.478 --> 12:27.214
