Thank you.

41:04.996 --> 41:06.665
Stop it. Come on, now.

41:14.005 --> 41:16.875
(laughing)

41:20.245 --> 41:21.146
That was awesome.

41:21.179 --> 41:22.748
Who knew George Tucker
could sing like that?

41:22.781 --> 41:23.815
Not me.

41:25.584 --> 41:27.786
So, did we cement your
status as indie rock chick?

41:27.819 --> 41:29.988
For another week, at least.

41:30.021 --> 41:32.724
But to be honest,
I kind of miss being

41:32.758 --> 41:35.861
